---

### F. Quality Comparison to Gold Standard (singer-songwriter level-03-first-notes.js)

**Rating: Matches or exceeds the gold standard**

The singer-songwriter level-03 is the comparison target. Let me evaluate:

| Dimension | SS Level 3 | Guitar Curriculum | Verdict |
|-----------|-----------|-------------------|---------|
| Step `why` depth | Excellent -- cites Gordon audiation, Dalcroze eurhythmics, constraint research | Excellent -- cites motor learning research, Edwin Gordon, sleep consolidation | **Tie** |
